<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link165718" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=165718&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F377190-i-was-wondering-if-the-books-follow-on-or%2Fanswers%2F165718-i-think-you-should">flag</a>
